like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"詩經係世界級都唔洗講到莎士比亞詩同白話文為基礎嘅現代文學一文不值㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d850cde06c61a544aa736f7f7ce2cc0d20e840","tid":140833,"uid":86833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"中國詩歌以抒情為主，外國文學多注重敘事同現實，各有特色。<br />\n<br />\n不過中國古詩高幾班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1fc5c0b12f2fd3b0e885b5893526abcccbb466","tid":140833,"uid":64775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好鍾意詩經個序<br />\n<br />\n「詩者，志之所之也。在心為志，發言為詩。情動於中，而形於言；言之不足，故嗟歎之；嗟歎之不足，故詠歌之；詠歌之不足，不知手之舞之足之蹈之也。」 <br />\n<br />\n可惜現代人已經失去呢種明明係本能嘅嘢<br />\n淨係識寫埋啲矯情鄺體文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五四運動ｏｎ９９<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實白話同舊文體可以共存<br />\n而家真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼讀文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係毛詩序<br />\n<br />\n詩經本來仲有齊 魯 韓幾家解詩 可惜無哂</blockquote><br />\n毛詩序淨係睇呢段就正，你真係認真睇番佢點解每一首詩，尤其係國風簡直屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b720016cee8d0d985270c0d818c75dfe4a7e87b","tid":140833,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好鍾意詩經個序<br />\n<br />\n「詩者，志之所之也。在心為志，發言為詩。情動於中，而形於言；言之不足，故嗟歎之；嗟歎之不足，故詠歌之；詠歌之不足，不知手之舞之足之蹈之也。」 <br />\n<br />\n可惜現代人已經失去呢種明明係本能嘅嘢<br />\n淨係識寫埋啲矯情鄺體文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五四運動ｏｎ９９<img src=\"/assets/faces