ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa3e332007cc7df6d1aa0de7a6cef4b47f77f6c","tid":140833,"uid":71188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:04:15.000Z","msg":"中四揀學科，我排文學尾2都俾我入到<br />\n讀左2年就drop左<br />\n當時覺得好無聊，又要背書咁背<br />\n好彩note冇掉<br />\n依家間唔中睇翻<br />\n先感受到古人文學水平係咁勁<br />\n每一詞一字，明明係同義詞<br />\n點解要用A字唔用B字<br />\n出黎嘅意景都差好遠"},{"pid":"ea63e3ba1eaba2fcbfd0f94078e34576035c17e1","tid":140833,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中四揀學科，我排文學尾2都俾我入到<br />\n讀左2年就drop左<br />\n當時覺得好無聊，又要背書咁背<br />\n好彩note冇掉<br />\n依家間唔中睇翻<br />\n先感受到古人文學水平係咁勁<br />\n每一詞一字，明明係同義詞<br />\n點解要用A字唔用B字<br />\n出黎嘅意景都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歐陽修 醉翁亭記<br />\n開首：環滁皆山也（平平平平仄）<br />\n第一句已經嚟料<br />\n連續四個平聲 <br />\n平聲特點係悠長清脆<br />\n連綿不斷、一望無際嘅山峰<br />\n形音結合<br />\n<br />\n個也字係上聲 <br />\n高低回環起伏嘅聲律效果<br />\n亦同山嘅形體相關<br />\n<br />\n原本係：滁州四面有山<br />\n改咗幾十次<br />\n也字用咗21次 而用咗25次<br />\n每次虛字運用嘅效果各異<br />\n唔好質疑古人文字功力"},{"pid":"1c909cf0f68653c135919cdc2f0d0bbd54741577","tid":140833,"uid":70459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:41:15.000Z","msg":"先言他物以引起所詠之詞。我欣賞詩經為後世中國文學打哂基礎，不過講佩服都係李商隱d隱晦詩，寫到好似文字密碼咁，唐詩格律，意境寫法用而家既新詩，係當時完全前衛。"},{"pid":"71f46b6fa4b4eee571d2270e9aaebfd37b830719","tid":140833,"uid":70459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好鍾意詩經個序<br />\n<br />\n「詩者，志之所之也。在心為志，發言為詩。情動於中，而形於言；言之不足，故嗟歎之；嗟歎之不足，故詠歌之；詠歌之不足，不知手之舞之足之蹈之也。」 <br />\n<br />\n可惜現代人已經失去呢種明明係本能嘅嘢<br />\n淨係識寫埋啲矯情鄺體文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五四運動ｏｎ９９<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實白話同舊文體可以共存<br />\n而家真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼讀文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家欣賞既地方已經唔同了，始終文學受西方影響太大"},{"pid":"320c7d67c4dce5eb7361359c95b5fc92512031aa","tid":140833,"uid":82576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"儒家興起後前秦呢種情詩真係買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e099e61942d8787ac7bbc54df3e62ef34b2d780","tid":140833,"uid":64898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先言他物以引起所詠之詞。我欣賞詩經為後世中國文學打哂基礎，不過講佩服都係李商隱d隱晦詩，寫到好似文字密碼咁，唐詩格律，意境寫法用而家既新詩，係當時完全前衛。</blockquote><br />\n到底而家有人解到&lt;錦瑟&gt;呢首詩未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee425c53259a3c9d32b5f8792a47f256476ce998","tid":140833,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夏之日，冬之夜<br />\n百歲之後，歸於其居<br />\n<br />\n冬之夜，夏之日<br />\n百歲之後，歸於其室<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n詩經最好的地方，係用字簡單<br />\n再簡單幾隻字砌到成個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能同民歌（風）有關<br />\n以前d 情歌咁有內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有巴打中意宋詞<br />\n但我覺得太堆砌<br />\n無詩經咁簡練得嚟情真意切"},{"pid":"a545ca69291f16f82b820f19c6dda2fa190fb70e","tid":140833,"uid":73410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"根本春秋時代啲人open好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後受儒家思想影響，寫野體材要關國家大事先係好，攪到啲嘢好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f32cc1f179febb281695b62fab954f8bce7d577","tid":140833,"uid":2750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"山無陵 江水為竭 冬雷震震 夏雨雪<br />\n天地合 敢乃與君絕<br />\n雖然唔出自詩經<br />\n但係好有印象"},{"pid":"e2a7e9a62a9874ff969283d5384a664603523c48","tid":140833,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"留"},{"pid":"bc1146cb9e7024a14e006632d2f8b23e48422b0e","tid":140833,"uid":420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"當年al 已經邊讀邊想像畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6facf0b00f08e312161dfa9441f8f9948128ad65","tid":140833,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山無陵 江水為竭 冬雷震震 夏雨雪<br />\n天地合 敢乃與君絕<br />\n雖然唔出自詩經<br />\n但係好有印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早期漢詩好好j ，仲好入腦易記，例如<br />\n<br />\n盈盈一水間，默默不得語"},{"pid":"b487482657374741cd6a6abfb550a5b0acaefa64","tid":140833,"uid":47341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"fa0e6549c58de491f1aae94c518243aafea39e47","tid":140833,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好鍾意詩經個序<br />\n<br />\n「詩者，志之所之也。在心為志，發言為詩。情動於中，而形於言；言之不足，故嗟歎之；嗟歎之不足，故詠歌之；詠歌之不足，不知手之舞之足之蹈之也。」 <br />\n<br />\n可惜現代人已經失去呢種明明係本能嘅嘢<br />\n淨係識寫埋啲矯情鄺體文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五四運動ｏｎ９９<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實白話同舊文體可以共存<br />\n而家真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼讀文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係五四運動on99，係我地on99<br />\n人地民國個陣既學者、學生，一樣都係出口成篇，文詞優美，文言文白話文都寫到勁正<br />\n<br />\n係共匪竊國之後無以為繼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f47b443b285e6aa8b7fc5cd76cdab826c3b845","tid":140833,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f54e5eeaa2f7222e248d0bf7d1f8a39d08ae758","tid":140833,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"留個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81207a13cf77a227742e282fd7edff6f73a5ed6e","tid":140833,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好鍾意詩經個序<br />\n<br />\n「詩者，志之所之也。在心為志，發言為詩。情動於中，而形於言；言之不足，故嗟歎之；嗟歎之不足，故詠歌之；詠歌之不足，不知手之舞之足之蹈之也。」 <br />\n<br />\n可惜現代人已經失去呢種明明係本能嘅嘢<br />\n淨係識寫埋啲矯情鄺體文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五四運動ｏｎ９９<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實白話同舊文體可以共存<br />\n而家真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼讀文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係五四運動on99，係我地on99<br />\n人地民國個陣既學者、學生，一樣都係出口成篇，文詞優美，文言文白話文都寫到勁正<br />\n<br />\n係共匪竊國之後無以為繼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小學初中背古文，高中先開始寫白話就最好<br />\n今時今日，咁樣只會比人話癡線，唔知關唔關新文化運動事喇"},{"pid":"392c348f89fe120ac900d1004d4644df33202038","tid":140833,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山無陵 江水為竭 冬雷震震 夏雨雪<br />\n天地合 敢乃與君絕<br />\n雖然唔出自詩經<br />\n但係好有印象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早期漢詩好好j ，仲好入腦易記，例如<br />\n盈盈一水間，默默不得語</blockquote><br />\n樂府唔少係民間曲辭<br />\n一係就文人學民歌來寫<br />\n咁自然唔會深得去邊"},{"pid":"7c309da009a60019ef8668ee1ba11117db587615","tid":140833,"uid":7708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"其實詩經好多都係與情慾性愛有關。例如上面都有嘅〈野有蔓草〉第二段：<br />\n<br />\n野有蔓草，零露瀼瀼。有美一人，婉如清颺。邂逅相遇，與子偕臧。<br />\n<br />\n朝早果陣喺草叢見到個靚女，邂逅相遇之後就一齊喱埋，唔知喱埋做咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，〈狡童〉：<br />\n<br />\n彼狡童兮，不與我食兮。維子之故，使我不能息兮。<br />\n<br />\n你呢個狡猾既人，唔餵飽我，我因為你，搞到不能將息。<br />\n<br />\n又，聞一多話詩經入面寫到魚嘅都係關於性愛。所以先秦時既文化可能比現代社會更開放。"},{"pid":"103c084575238652fa9db61f458b32db04b8b0c7","tid":140833,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實詩經好多都係與情慾性愛有關。例如上面都有嘅〈野有蔓草〉第二段：<br />\n<br />\n野有蔓草，零露瀼瀼。有美一人，婉如清颺。邂逅相遇，與子偕臧。<br />\n<br />\n朝早果陣喺草叢見到個靚女，邂逅相遇之後就一齊喱埋，唔知喱埋做咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，〈狡童〉：<br />\n<br />\n彼狡童兮，不與我食兮。維子之故，使我不能息兮。<br />\n<br />\n你呢個狡猾既人，唔餵飽我，我因為你，搞到不能將息。<br />\n<br />\n又，聞一多話詩經入面寫到魚嘅都係關於性愛。所以先秦時既文化可能比現代社會更開放。</blockquote><br />\n外儒內法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d8e00fd8480752aec5ed75b6dadb66d981a41","tid":140833,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同英文比咪又係垃圾，唔好在吹奏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文完全整唔出個意境</blockquote><br />\n雖然佢係鳩up，但其實西方文學嘅詩都唔係無意境。<br />\n也斯余光中都引用過唔少西方詩人嘅詩作嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d95b53608bc74ca6fb651591aad6f6e2ceb927e","tid":140833,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同英文比咪又係垃圾，唔好在吹奏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文d詩真係唔識欣賞得罪講句</blockquote><br />\n真係唔識欣賞莎士比亞啲濕鳩詩<br />\n又無意景，讀出嚟又唔好聽</blockquote><br />\n莎士比亞sonnet九成都係串鳩人嘅satire，咁當然無乜意景，你應該睇下Auden T.S. Eliot之類，其實Thomas Hardy都唔錯。<br />\n要景靚可以睇下romanticism嘅詩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704f4b53b236c3ef8d889f213c99d05055bf7fa5","tid":140833,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"詩經啲用詞好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659cc94f7e2977e172613e9d077014a44ae5f27f","tid":140833,"uid":69279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實睇返古人啲名都好有意境<br />\n邊似而家周街都係呀晴 呀希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a8c3d94dd3d7fcb8fba1c14b98d80296b556b8","tid":140833,"uid":70997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"9782206268cf2b135e3194187e0cd3d249bf33a4","tid":140833,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"492f42956b7ddb37e3a49c1832ada19dc15d9517","tid":140833,"uid":82639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"有啲野，讀書真係無理解。<br />\n下面呢首詩，近年真係好大提醒，就黎三張野.... <br />\n<br />\n勸君莫惜金縷衣，<br />\n勸君惜取少年時。 <br />\n花開堪折直須折，<br />\n莫待無花空折枝。"}]}